  <thing id="fImpSight" name="Improved Sight" description="You have learned deep secrets of time&apos;s flow, and your vision is rarely wrong.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Glimpse the Flow, Character level 6th\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: The insight bonus from Glimpse the Flow increases to +4\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Glimpse the Flow provides a +2 insight bonus" compset="Feat" summary="Insight bonus from Glimpse the Flow increases to +4">
