  <thing id="fGrSight" name="Greater Sight" description="Years of experience have taught you how best to interpret your visions, the future holds little mystery for you.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Glimpse the Flow, Improved Sight, Character level 12th\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: The insight bonus from Glimpse the Flow increases to +6\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: Glimpse the Flow provides a +2 insight bonus" compset="Feat" summary="Insight bonus from Glimpse the Flow increases to +6">
