  <thing id="fFarsight" name="Farsight" description="Through rigorous mental discipline, you have learned to peer farther into the ebbs and flows of the River of Time.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Glimpse the Flow\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration, to 2 rounds\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: The duration of Glimpse the Flow is 1 round" compset="Feat" summary="Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration, to 2 rounds" uniqueness="useronce">
