  <thing id="fIFarsight" name="Improved Farsight" description="Through rigorous mental discipline, you have discovered a way to anchor your mind to the present so you may safely peer even farther upstream. \n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Glimpse the Flow, Farsight\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration again, to 4 rounds\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: The duration of Glimpse the Flow is 1 round" compset="Feat" summary="Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration, to 4 rounds">
