  <thing id="fGFarsight" name="Greater Farsight" description="Through rigorous mental discipline, you have strengthened your mental anchor, allowing you to venture even farther afield. \n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Glimpse the Flow, Farsight, Improved Farsight\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration again, to 8 rounds\n\n{b}Normal{/b}: The duration of Glimpse the Flow is 1 round" compset="Feat" summary="Your Glimpse the Flow ability doubles in duration, to 8 rounds">
