  <thing id="rHumPale" name="Human (Paleface)" description="Paleface is the term boulmaukans use to refer to the light skinned peoples of the various colonies founded by Ansalonian powers. They range from blond haired and blue eyed Solamnians to hook-nosed and curly haired descendants of Ishtar." compset="Race">
