  <thing id="rChaWindRi" name="Chaos Windrider" description="The Chaos twisted these two allies so that they are literally inseparable. The Silvanesti was combined at the waist to his griffin companion, creating a centaurian creature. The once proud elf&#146;s skin is a dusty grey pallor with a mucus like membrane covering it. The griffin&#146;s fur is falling out in tufts, revealing shiny scales underneath and its tail is a meager skeletal remains. The most drastic change is its wings, the feathers all sway with a semblance of sentience, wanting to grasp anything that comes to close and drain life force from the unfortunate victim. The Elf&#146;s face is twisted in pain and his eyes glow with a malice matching the most blood-hungry beasts.\n\nThis creature resides in its old eyrie, protecting it from anything that would approach. It surprises its&#146; target from the air, ripping it apart with its claws before the abominable wings grab it and suck the living soul out of the creature." compset="Race">
