  <thing id="ioFaiDrMas" name="Fai&apos;lon&apos;s Dragon Mask" description="This specially enchanted dragon mask is essential to the Farseer&apos;s passing unobserved. Like a {i}mask of lies{/i}, it grants the wearer a +5 competence bonus to Bluff &amp; constant {i}undetectable alignment{/i}, and like a {i}dragon mask{/i} it enables the wearer to {i}see invisibility{/i} 2 times per day as a swift action for 5 minutes each. \n\nIt also possesses the unique ability to conceal any number of magical auras that the wearer is in contact with, as {i}Nystul&apos;s magic aura{/i}, though any items set down detect normally after 10 rounds. This effect, when combined with her custom {i}greater alter self{/i} spell, allowed her to pass as any number of mundane people." compset="Wondrous" uniqueness="unique">
