  <thing id="isFeldCane" name="Felden&apos;s Cane (Staff of Divination)" description="Made from a supple length of willow, often with a forked tip, this staff allows use of the following spells:\n\n&#149; Detect secret doors (1 charge)\n&#149; Locate object (1 charge)\n&#149; Tongues (1 charge)\n&#149; Locate creature (2 charges)\n&#149; Prying eyes (2 charges)\n&#149; True seeing (3 charges)\n\nStrong divination; CL 13th; Craft Staff, detect secret doors, locate creature, locate object, prying eyes, tongues, true seeing; Price 73,500 gp." compset="Staff">
