    <eval phase="Render" index="4">hero.child[xParalyze].field[CustDesc].text = &quot;A monstrous slug&#146;s body secretes an anaesthetizing slime. A target hit by a monstrous slug&#146;s bite, grapple, or trample attack must succeed on a Fortitude save or be paralyzed for 3d6 rounds. The save DC is Constitution-based.&quot;</eval>
