  <thing id="ioRapCasIn" name="Circlet of Rapid Casting, +2 Intelligence" description="{b}Price (Item Level){/b}: 15,000 gp (14th)\n{b}Body Slot{/b}: Head\n{b}Caster Level{/b}: 11th\n{b}Aura{/b}: Moderate; (DC 20) transmutation\n{b}Activation{/b}: Swift (command)\n{b}Weight{/b}: &#151;\n\n{i}This golden circlet is engraved with dozens of different symbols and runes{/i}.\n\nA {i}circlet of rapid casting{/i} allows you to cast a small number of spells each day more quickly. This circlet has 3 charges, which are renewed each day at dawn. Spending 1 or more charges allows you to cast a single spell as part of the same swift action you used to activate the circlet. This spell must be one that normally has a casting time of no longer than 1 standard action. Doing this expends the prepared spell or spell slot as if you had cast the spell normally.\n\n{i}1 charge{/i}: Cast a single spell of up to 2nd level.\n{i}2 charges{/i}: Cast a single spell of up to 3rd level.\n{i}3 charges{/i}: Cast a single spell of up to 4th level.\n\n{i}Prerequisites{/i}: Craft Wondrous Item, Quicken Spell.\n\n{i}Cost to Create{/i}: 7,500 gp, 600 XP, 15 days." compset="Wondrous">
