  <thing id="tmRemnant" name="Remnant" description="These lobotomized warriors have had most of their essences withdrawn and their best abilities harvested. They are similar to trained animals, but retain the much of the combat prowess they possessed prior to the operation. They move slowly but powerfully and are extremely tough.\n\nLose all racial abilities, including ability modifiers, HD change to d12s, recalculate skill points based on new intelligence (shifting to Climb, Jump, Swim, Hide, Move Silently, Ride, Spot and Listen). Feats remain unchanged (and ignore pre-requisites)." compset="Template" uniqueness="unique">
